{"tid":716713,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大個睇返 發覺港台節目真係幾高質","createTime":"2018-06-25T13:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T09:36:49.000Z","uid":172607,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18a352822bdedad36d9da84bdd2220d06fcdfcb2","tid":716713,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"細個睇都唔覺有咩特別<br />\n大個睇發覺港台節目真心拍得好過cctvb膠劇好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n表達嘅野好符合當時社會現況（MK時代）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c7upYRtur6o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc7upYRtur6o&d=jsHclFwkGOfsOFaFZTPjEJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a5e398de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c7upYRtur6o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PUlgez759Fk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPUlgez759Fk&d=jsHclFwkGOfsOFaFZTPjEJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9ef18fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PUlgez759Fk</a><br />\n<br />\nMK仔女反叛時期<br />\n戀愛大過天 扑野唔理後果<br />\n有左就落左佢 大個就搵毒撚埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然MK仔都有好人嘅<br />\n第二集01:12 果句「緊係生啦！我做司機搵$8000一個月！」<br />\n而家呢個年代當然會話窮人唔好生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢都算係一個敢作敢為嘅真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMK仔不斷講 我最愛你一個 唔會一腳踏兩船<br />\n最後結果當然係中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年都係一個循環咁loop緊<br />\n<br />\n希望而家呢個年代嘅後生女識得帶眼識人 潔身自愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想第日連登巴打幫你地埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe45d0545b9464b4a5a685b93d3cb24d8d7e725e","tid":716713,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"仲要有Venus 黃敏奕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5c4bcef178c9cee68b25b7570073c479a33756","tid":716713,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"敏奕bb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b3b0b2f57d534640e4cb48f5fb9c5aa11bbd96","tid":716713,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87820efdc47740287b005e0592cd6781283867ab","tid":716713,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b3b0b2f57d534640e4cb48f5fb9c5aa11bbd96","tid":716713,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe45d0545b9464b4a5a685b93d3cb24d8d7e725e","tid":716713,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"仲要有Venus 黃敏奕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"如果打手 標題應該會寫明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4acd3b8639b6fa1bf19da20779d1cc762036a8","tid":716713,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited